quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,57,"maa ki wi'a: "Si Alah feewnuno kam, mi wonanyno jiyaa…óo e gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen"."
  39,58,"Maa ki wi'a, tuma ki yi'ata lepte …óen: "Si fehre ruttagol no woodannoo kam, mi jeyee e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen"."
  39,59,""Gasataa ! Tawde aayeeje Am …óen aruno e maa…óa, njeddu…óaa …óe, mawnintini…óaa, laati…óaa jiyaa…óo e yeddu…ďe …ďeen"."
  39,60,"√Ďande Darngal, a yi'oya fennonoo…ďe e hoore Allah …ďen, hino …ďawli je'ece. Wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaa∆īorde mawnintinii…ďe …ďeen?"
  39,61,"Allah na da…óndira gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen, sabu maloore ma…ď…ďe nden. Bone memataa …ďeen, wonaa kam…ďe ngoni sunoytoo…ďe."
  39,62,"Ko Allah woni Tak…óo kala hu'unde, ko KaŇčko kadi woni pawtii…óo kala hu'unde."
  39,63,"Ko KaŇčko sottir…óe kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin woodani. Yeddu…ďe aayeeje Allah …ďeen non, ko …ďen ngoni hayru…ďe(pertu…ďe) …ďen."
  39,64,"Maaku: "E ko woori Allah, njamirton mi, yo mi rew, onon …ďee majju…ďe?""
  39,65,"GooŇč…óii wahayinaama e maa…óa, e …ďen adinoo…ďe ma: "Si a sirkii, pellet, golle maa …óeen bonay njeyi…óaa e hayru…ďe …ďeen."
  39,66,"Alah rew Allah, njeye…óaa e yettoo…ďe (Mo) …ďen."
  39,67,"∆Āe mawniniraani Allah, no O foti maninireede, hara le, leydi ndin fof, ko tamannde makko, √Ďande Darngal, kammuuji …óin kadi taggiree √Īaamo makko. Senayee woodanii Mo ! O toowii e kon ko …ďe cirkanta mo."